{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Jas|1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","chapter":1,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":1,"text":"James, a servant of God and of the Lord Jesus Christ:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":2,"text":"Consider it a great joy, my brothers and sisters, whenever you experience various trials,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":3,"text":"because you know that the testing of your faith produces endurance.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":4,"text":"And let endurance have its full effect, so that you may be mature and complete, lacking nothing.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":5,"text":"Now if any of you lacks wisdom, he should ask God —who gives to all generously and ungrudgingly —and it will be given to him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":6,"text":"But let him ask in faith without doubting. For the doubter is like the surging sea, driven and tossed by the wind.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":7,"text":"That person should not expect to receive anything from the Lord,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":8,"text":"being double-minded and unstable in all his ways.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":9,"text":"Let the brother of humble circumstances boast in his exaltation,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":10,"text":"but let the rich boast in his humiliation because he will pass away like a flower of the field.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":11,"text":"For the sun rises and, together with the scorching wind, dries up the grass; its flower falls off, and its beautiful appearance perishes. In the same way, the rich person will wither away while pursuing his activities.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":12,"text":"Blessed is the one who endures trials, because when he has stood the test he will receive the crown of life that God has promised to those who love him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":13,"text":"No one undergoing a trial should say, “I am being tempted by God,” since God is not tempted by evil, and he himself doesn’t tempt anyone.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":14,"text":"But each person is tempted when he is drawn away and enticed by his own evil desire.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":15,"text":"Then after desire has conceived, it gives birth to sin, and when sin is fully grown, it gives birth to death.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":16,"text":"Don’t be deceived, my dear brothers and sisters.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":17,"text":"Every good and perfect gift is from above, coming down from the Father of lights, who does not change like shifting shadows.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":18,"text":"By his own choice, he gave us birth by the word of truth so that we would be a kind of firstfruits of his creatures.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":19,"text":"My dear brothers and sisters, understand this: Everyone should be quick to listen, slow to speak, and slow to anger,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":20,"text":"for human anger does not accomplish God’s righteousness.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":21,"text":"Therefore, ridding yourselves of all moral filth and the evil that is so prevalent, humbly receive the implanted word, which is able to save your souls.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":22,"text":"But be doers of the word and not hearers only, deceiving yourselves.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":23,"text":"Because if anyone is a hearer of the word and not a doer, he is like someone looking at his own face in a mirror.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":24,"text":"For he looks at himself, goes away, and immediately forgets what kind of person he was.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":25,"text":"But the one who looks intently into the perfect law of freedom and perseveres in it, and is not a forgetful hearer but a doer who works —this person will be blessed in what he does.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":26,"text":"If anyone thinks he is religious without controlling his tongue, his religion is useless and he deceives himself.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","bookOrder":58,"chapter":1,"verse":27,"text":"Pure and undefiled religion before God the Father is this: to look after orphans and widows in their distress and to keep oneself unstained from the world.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Jas","chapter":1,"paragraphStarts":[1,2,5,9,12,13,16,19,22,26],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Greeting"},{"beforeVerse":2,"text":"Trials and Maturity"},{"beforeVerse":19,"text":"Hearing and Doing the Word"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"James, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:55","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":55,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 6:3","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 12:17","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:13","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":13,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 21:18","book":"Act","chapter":21,"verse":18,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:19","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":19,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 2:9","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 2:12","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:1","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" a servant of God "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:17","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":17,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:1","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 6:6","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":6,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 1:1","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:16","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":16,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:1","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"o"},{"kind":"text","text":" and of the Lord Jesus Christ:"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 13:55","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":55},{"label":"Mk 6:3","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":3},{"label":"Ac 12:17","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":17},{"label":"Ac 15:13","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":13},{"label":"Ac 21:18","book":"Act","chapter":21,"verse":18},{"label":"Gl 1:19","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":19},{"label":"Gl 2:9","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":9},{"label":"Gl 2:12","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":12},{"label":"Jd 1:1","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Ac 16:17","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":17},{"label":"Rm 1:1","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Eph 6:6","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":6},{"label":"Jms 1:1","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"1Pt 2:16","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":16},{"label":"Rv 1:1","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Consider it a great joy, my brothers and sisters, whenever you experience various trials, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:12","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:6","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 5:12","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":12},{"label":"1Pt 1:6","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"because you know that the testing of your faith produces endurance. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And let endurance have its full effect, so that you may be mature and complete, lacking nothing."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now if any of you lacks wisdom, he should ask God —who gives to all generously and ungrudgingly —and it will be given to him. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 3:9","book":"1Ki","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 2:3–6","book":"Pro","chapter":2,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:7","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Kg 3:9","book":"1Ki","chapter":3,"verse":9},{"label":"Pr 2:3–6","book":"Pro","chapter":2,"verse":3},{"label":"Mt 7:7","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But let him ask in faith without doubting. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or without divided loyalties"},{"kind":"text","text":" For the doubter is like the surging sea, driven and tossed by the wind. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or without divided loyalties"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"That person should not expect to receive anything from the Lord, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"being double-minded and unstable in all his ways. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or in all his conduct"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 4:8","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:14","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jms 4:8","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":8},{"label":"2Pt 2:14","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or in all his conduct"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Let the brother of humble circumstances boast in his exaltation, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"but let the rich boast in his humiliation because he will pass away like a flower of the field. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 7:31","book":"1Co","chapter":7,"verse":31,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:24","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 7:31","book":"1Co","chapter":7,"verse":31},{"label":"1Pt 1:24","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For the sun rises and, together with the scorching wind, dries up the grass; its flower falls off, and its beautiful appearance perishes. In the same way, the rich person will wither away while pursuing his activities. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 102:4","book":"Psa","chapter":102,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 102:11","book":"Psa","chapter":102,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 40:7","book":"Isa","chapter":40,"verse":7,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 102:4","book":"Psa","chapter":102,"verse":4},{"label":"Ps 102:11","book":"Psa","chapter":102,"verse":11},{"label":"Is 40:7","book":"Isa","chapter":40,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Blessed is the one who endures trials, because when he has stood the test he will receive the crown "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:25","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 4:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:4","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 2:10","book":"Rev","chapter":2,"verse":10,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 3:11","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" of life that God "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read that the Lord"},{"kind":"text","text":" has promised to those who love him. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:22","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":22,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:5","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"g"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 9:25","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":25},{"label":"2Tm 4:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":4,"verse":8},{"label":"1Pt 5:4","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":4},{"label":"Rv 2:10","book":"Rev","chapter":2,"verse":10},{"label":"Rv 3:11","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":11},{"label":"Mt 10:22","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":22},{"label":"Jms 2:5","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read that the Lord"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"No one undergoing a trial should say, “I am being tempted by God,” since God is not tempted by evil, and he himself doesn’t tempt anyone. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But each person is tempted when he is drawn away and enticed by his own evil desire. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 7:6–23","book":"Pro","chapter":7,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 7:6–23","book":"Pro","chapter":7,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then after desire has conceived, it gives birth to sin, and when sin is fully grown, it gives birth to death. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 15:35","book":"Job","chapter":15,"verse":35,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 7:14","book":"Psa","chapter":7,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 59:4","book":"Isa","chapter":59,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 6:23","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":23,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 15:35","book":"Job","chapter":15,"verse":35},{"label":"Ps 7:14","book":"Psa","chapter":7,"verse":14},{"label":"Is 59:4","book":"Isa","chapter":59,"verse":4},{"label":"Rm 6:23","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Don’t be deceived, my dear brothers and sisters. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 6:9","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 1:19","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 6:9","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":9},{"label":"Jms 1:19","book":"Jas","chapter":1,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Every good and perfect gift is from above, coming down from the Father of lights, who does not change like shifting shadows. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 23:19","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mal 3:6","book":"Mal","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 3:27","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":27,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 1:5","book":"1Jn","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 23:19","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":19},{"label":"Mal 3:6","book":"Mal","chapter":3,"verse":6},{"label":"Jn 3:27","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":27},{"label":"1Jn 1:5","book":"1Jn","chapter":1,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"By his own choice, he gave us birth by the word of truth so that we would be a kind of firstfruits of his creatures. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:13","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:12","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":12,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 1:13","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":13},{"label":"Eph 1:12","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"My dear brothers and sisters, understand this: Everyone should be quick to listen, slow to speak, and slow to anger, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 10:19","book":"Pro","chapter":10,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 17:27","book":"Pro","chapter":17,"verse":27,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ec 5:1–2","book":"Ecc","chapter":5,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 10:19","book":"Pro","chapter":10,"verse":19},{"label":"Pr 17:27","book":"Pro","chapter":17,"verse":27},{"label":"Ec 5:1–2","book":"Ecc","chapter":5,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"for human anger does not accomplish God’s righteousness. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, ridding yourselves of all moral filth and the evil that is so prevalent, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or the abundance of evil"},{"kind":"text","text":" humbly receive the implanted word, which is able to save your souls. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:13","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:22","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:8","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":8,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 1:13","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":13},{"label":"Eph 4:22","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":22},{"label":"Col 3:8","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or the abundance of evil"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 7:24–27","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 2:13","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:14","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" be doers of the word and not hearers only, deceiving yourselves. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 7:24–27","book":"Mat","chapter":7,"verse":24},{"label":"Rm 2:13","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":13},{"label":"Jms 2:14","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Because if anyone is a hearer of the word and not a doer, he is like someone looking at his own face "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or at his natural face"},{"kind":"text","text":" in a mirror. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or at his natural face"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For he looks at himself, goes away, and immediately forgets what kind of person he was. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the one who looks intently into the perfect law of freedom and perseveres in it, and is not a forgetful hearer but a doer who works —this person will be blessed in what he does. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 13:17","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:12","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 13:17","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":17},{"label":"Jms 2:12","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If anyone "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add among you"},{"kind":"text","text":" thinks he is religious without controlling his tongue, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 34:13","book":"Psa","chapter":34,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 39:1","book":"Psa","chapter":39,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 141:3","book":"Psa","chapter":141,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 3:2","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":2,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:10","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" his religion is useless and he deceives himself. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 34:13","book":"Psa","chapter":34,"verse":13},{"label":"Ps 39:1","book":"Psa","chapter":39,"verse":1},{"label":"Ps 141:3","book":"Psa","chapter":141,"verse":3},{"label":"Jms 3:2","book":"Jas","chapter":3,"verse":2},{"label":"1Pt 3:10","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add among you"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jas:1:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Pure and undefiled religion before God the Father is this: to look after orphans and widows "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 31:17","book":"Job","chapter":31,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:17","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:23","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":23,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 25:36","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":36,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" in their distress and to keep oneself unstained from the world. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 12:2","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":2,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 5:18","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":18,"letter":"f"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 31:17","book":"Job","chapter":31,"verse":17},{"label":"Is 1:17","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":17},{"label":"Is 1:23","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":23},{"label":"Mt 25:36","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":36},{"label":"Rm 12:2","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":2},{"label":"1Jn 5:18","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099560614}